Note: Test lists, index access, classes, objects

Note: Lists and index access
items = [10, 20, 30]
Print items[0]
Print items[2]

Note: Functions
Function double takes x
    Return x * 2
End

Print double(5)
Print double(21)

Note: For range with math
total = 0
For i from 1 to 100
    Increase total by i
End
Print total

Note: String operations
name = "EPL"
Print name
Print name + " is " + "powerful!"

Note: Assert
Assert 2 + 2 == 4
Assert 100 - 1 == 99

Print "All features compiled!"
